{"tid":1537613,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"［街頭偽術］撐Popo Street Art","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T10:26:12.000Z","uid":31082,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1219465ef8423651faee93985c145a18afa08ad4","tid":1537613,"uid":31082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:46:05.000Z","msg":"支持香港成立 中立 可信 獨立調查委員會還警察「清白」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vu9Eubd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVu9Eubd.png&h=48fa03fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊集思廣益諗吓可以點從street art方面向市民大眾宣傳警察嘅日常工作，從而改善部分人對現今警隊嘅誤解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d588d0de144bf23a29aab27a5e1cd7ed7bd18c","tid":1537613,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce7f8e8ee9f3a60229cf8e5e14021ff68c75010e","tid":1537613,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月6日 反濫捕 抗威權集會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535223</a>"},{"pid":"511e8bdf5ac2cac9d41bd888512e668f77d2d9f7","tid":1537613,"uid":31082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b5cb1a61a38c233f0904deddceea7e983ee900","tid":1537613,"uid":31082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce2241067917588d1f7b3d08897211f58e0da9c","tid":1537613,"uid":31082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c8417735a2d8fd854f3c80ab9a24ab5024779a4","tid":1537613,"uid":31082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8fed769b074a926032ebf1702d1e77a09afad7b","tid":1537613,"uid":31082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"